                  <story-point caption='The chart shows how sales performed over time.&#10;Sales showed variability across periods, with a sharp decline recently.&#10;This trend could indicate shifts in customer demand or external market factors.' captured-sheet='Sheet 5' id='1' />
                  <story-point caption='This map highlights the distribution of sales across different cities.&#10;Higher sales concentration in certain regions indicates strong market presence and customer demand.&#10;&#10;' captured-sheet='Sheet 6' id='2'>
